title: One Bedroom Available! Wilshire/Grove Area! Id#7

posting_body: ['Vintage style 1 bedroom apartment are available!', 'Located in one of the best areas of LA.', 'Walking distance to Trader Joes, LACMA, the Grove, La Tropezianne, Republique, Odys & Penelope, and more.', 'Plus, just a hop skip and a jump to Hollywood, Griffith Park, or DTLA.', "You'll love this beautiful building, and the tree-lined street.", 'The apartment features exposed brick and generous closets.', 'There is a great view, large windows, with a lot of natural light during the day.', 'The newly, renovated kitchen is great for cooking and entertaining and contains top-of-the-line cabinetry, countertops, and custom flooring.', 'Newly renovated appliances included Ceiling fans, Large Windows/Natural Light!', 'AMENITIES: Fitness Center, Cinema Room, Pool Table, BBQ, and Fire Pit as well!', 'Details/Logistics:', "Deposit: One month's rent", 'Pet Deposit: $200.00', 'One Time Pet Fee: $100.00', 'Application Fee: $40.00', 'Owner Paid Utilities: Gas', 'Tenant Paid Utilities: Electric, water, trash and sewage', 'Laundry Onsite', 'Street Parking', 'Parking Lots Nearby:', '- District La Brea (181 South La Brea Ave)', '- 5670 Wilshire Blvd.', '- 5200 Wilshire Blvd.', '* Square footage may not be exact.', 'Square footages are based on estimates from model units.', '** Marketing pictures may not be of the actual unit.', 'Units do not come with furniture.', '***Application, Admin, and security deposit fees subject to change', '****$2.83 city SCEP fee added to monthly rent']
